  "title": "Social Media Marketing Executive (Content & On-Camera)",
  "description": "<h3><strong>Roles &amp; Responsibilities</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Plan, create, and manage engaging content across social media platforms (Facebook, Instagram, TikTok, YouTube, etc.).</li>\n  <li>Act as the <strong>on-camera talent</strong> for product promotion videos, lifestyle shoots, and brand campaigns.</li>\n  <li>Work with the team to script, shoot, and edit short-form videos and creative content.</li>\n  <li>Monitor and analyze social media performance to improve engagement and reach.</li>\n  <li>Research and stay updated on current social media trends, especially in video content.</li>\n  <li>Support marketing campaigns, events, and collaborations with influencers.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><strong>Job Offers &amp; Benefits</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Attractive basic salary with performance incentives.</li>\n  <li>Career growth opportunities in digital marketing &amp; branding.</li>\n  <li>Transport / mobile allowance may be provided.</li>\n  <li>Fun and creative working environment with hands-on content projects.</li>\n  <li>Training in video production and social media tools will be provided.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><strong>Candidate Role</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Be both a <strong>social media marketer</strong> and <strong>brand ambassador</strong>.</li>\n  <li>Take part in video shoots and bring energy/personality to the brand.</li>\n  <li>Build strong brand presence through creative storytelling.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><strong>Job Scope</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Manage daily posting, scheduling, and interaction on social media accounts.</li>\n  <li>Participate in <strong>video shoots</strong> (product features, lifestyle content, creative skits).</li>\n  <li>Work with content creator/video editor to produce engaging campaigns.</li>\n  <li>Track analytics, prepare reports, and propose improvements.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><strong>Job Requirements</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Diploma in Marketing, Mass Communication, Media, or related field (or equivalent experience).</li>\n  <li>Comfortable <strong>appearing on camera</strong> and able to act/present naturally in videos.</li>\n  <li>Familiar with TikTok, Instagram Reels, and short-form video trends.</li>\n  <li>Creative, energetic, and passionate about digital marketing.</li>\n  <li>Knowledge of basic video editing or Canva/Photoshop will be an advantage.</li>\n  <li>Fresh graduates or entry-level candidates with strong interest in social media are welcome.</li>\n</ul>",
